<br>
;P<br>
<br>
Seriously tho, I have used mezz to win fights I would never have had a chance in otherwise.  I have used mezz to run away from a red/grape mob that I accidently got into aggro range.<br>
<br>
Would I give mezz up for something of equal value?  Sure!  But consider CC rules the day (for the most part) so it would have to be a pretty hefty addition to give up mezz.  Also, mezz is an insta.  The AF chant you mentioned sounds like it would run INSTEAD of my DA.  I dont need more chants at the expense of instas UNLESS I can run multiple chants.<br>
<br>
Thats my 2 tattered woolen vests anyway.<br>
